summary: Turns Ben Erai Palace (from the amazing mod The Gray Cowl of Nocturnal by Manny GT) into a player home, also adds another player home and small lake outside Ben Erai, and a tropical style island off the shore of Solstheim.
descriptionHtml: Turns Ben Erai Palace (from the amazing mod The Gray Cowl of Nocturnal by Manny GT) into a player home, also adds another player home and small lake outside Ben Erai, and a tropical style island off the shore of Solstheim, finally I added a cooking pot and a basement to the buyable Ben Erai player home.
author: Manny GT
